import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { UserService } from 'src/app/services/user.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-add-user', templateUrl: './add-user.component.html', styleUrls: ['./add-user.component.css'] }) export class AddUserComponent { constructor(private userService: UserService) { } user = { username: '', password: '', firstName: '', lastName: '', email: '', role: '' } addUser() { this.userService.registerUser(this.user).subscribe((res) => { alert(res); this.user.username = ''; this.user.password = ''; this.user.firstName = ''; this.user.lastName = ''; this.user.email = ''; this.user.role = ''; }) } } Document
